text: Tepoxteco is a town of the municipality Chicontepec de Tejeda, in the state of Veracruz, eastern Mexico.Instituto Nacional de Estadística y Geografía. Principales resultados por localidad 2010 (ITER). Retrieved on December 23, 2008 This town has got 462 inhabitants,Municipio de Chicontepec many people still speak the nahuatl language. ==References== Category:Populated places in Veracruz
